    "Description": "Interested in doing a little hunting? \n\n~mission(TargetName) sabotaged one of our fuel shipments and cost us a ton of creds, so I\u2019m looking for someone to make \u2018em pay for what they did. Just got word ~mission(TargetName|Last) was spotted at ~mission(Location|Address). If you head there now, there\u2019s a good chance you can pick up their trail and take \u2018em out for good. \n\n~mission(TargetName|Last) didn\u2019t work alone, so don\u2019t be surprised if they\u2019re traveling with extra protection.\n\n- Smokey",
    "DisplayDescription": "Interested in doing a little hunting? \n\n[TargetName] sabotaged one of our fuel shipments and cost us a ton of creds, so I\u2019m looking for someone to make \u2018em pay for what they did. Just got word [TargetName|Last] was spotted at [Location|Address]. If you head there now, there\u2019s a good chance you can pick up their trail and take \u2018em out for good. \n\n[TargetName|Last] didn\u2019t work alone, so don\u2019t be surprised if they\u2019re traveling with extra protection.\n\n- Smokey",
